summary:
Marvel characters as things my friends and I have said
Peter: whats the plural of moose? 
Ned:...
Ned: meese
Peter: right!?...
body:
Marvel characters as things my friends and I have said

Peter: whats the plural of moose?

Ned:…

Ned: meese

Peter: right!? Because the plural of goose is geese, so moose must be meese!

-Steve: What’s soya sauce made out of?

Thor:…

Thor: fish

Steve:…

Bruce: Isnt it made out of soya beans?

Sam: Im pretty sure its like pure salt

Nat: I think its soya beans

Bucky: Yeah, that makes sense *nods*

Steve:…

Steve: ok

-Steve, to Nat: Why do you think your bi?

Tony, also to Nat: Yeah, like, did u just look at boobs and go “yummy!”?

-Peter: *starts bleeding*

Peter: Should I drink it?

MJ: Yes. Drink it like the vampire you are.

Peter: *licks blood*

Peter: …

Peter: Its salty

MJ: Salty?

Peter: Yeah. Like metal.

MJ: Y'know maybe thats because of the iron in your blood

Peter: But its…

Peter: Saltier.

-Hope: We could’ve been done 10 minutes ago!

Scott: But ya didn’t

-Mantis: *looks at gravel they’re standing on*

Mantis: Y'know rocks have feelings

Gaurdians: …

Mantis: And genders

-Shuri: Plants know when they’re being eaten.

T'challa: What?! No! Why would you tell me that, I’m trying to be vegetarian!

Bonus:

Loki, disguised as Odin: before we murder these children we must praise our lord and savior, Loki
